## ‚úÖ LOCATION 8: HOMEWORLD PORTAL
### "The Final Choice"

**Environment Type:** Otherworldly - Reality Nexus  
**Time:** Beyond time  
**Condition:** Alien dimension gateway  
**NPC:** Xyloth's Avatar (The Gatekeeper)

### Visual Design
