## VIVERSE Deployment Notes

### WebGL Optimization
- **Texture Compression:** Reduce all textures for browser
- **Polygon Reduction:** LOD systems on complex models
- **Light Baking:** Pre-bake lighting where possible
- **Occlusion Culling:** Enable for all scenes
- **Audio Compression:** Compressed audio formats

### Performance Targets
- **FPS:** Minimum 30 FPS on mid-range hardware
- **Load Times:** Under 10 seconds per scene
- **Memory:** Keep under 2GB total

